{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.key()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><em><code>key()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスの <code>key()</code> メソッドは数値 n を渡すと、ストレージ内で n 番目のキーの名称を返します。キーの順序はユーザエージェント依存であり、この順序に頼るべきではありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>aKeyName</em> = <em>storage</em>.key(<em>key</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"key\"><em>key</em></dt>\n <dd>名称を取得したいキーの番号を表す整数。これは 0 から始まるインデックスです。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>キーの名称を持つ <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数は、ローカルストレージのキー全体に対して反復処理を行います:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">forEachKey</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">key</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>注記</strong>: 実際の例として、<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-storage-demo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-storage-key\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">key() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.key","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API を使用する</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザ実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Storage インターフェイスの key() メソッドは数値 n を渡すと、ストレージ内で n 番目のキーの名称を返します。キーの順序はユーザエージェント依存であり、この順序に頼るべきではありません。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage.key()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/storage/key","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/storage/key/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage","title":"Storage"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key","title":"Storage.key()"}],"pageTitle":"Storage.key() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}